<i>noun</i>: 흥정 [흥정] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>흥정 [흥정]</dt><br>
<dd>1. bargaining</dd><br>
<dd>물건을 사고팖.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of selling and buying products.</dd><br>
<dd>2. negotiation</dd><br>
<dd>물건을 사거나 팔기 위해 품질이나 가격 등을 의논함.</dd><br>
<dd>To discuss quality, price, etc., to buy or sell products.</dd><br>
<dd>3. negotiating</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 문제를 자기에게 조금이라도 더 유리하도록 상대방과 말을 주고받음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of engaging in a dialogue on an issue in a way that benefits oneself more than the other person.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>